dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Bayfield County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represent hydrography for Bayfield County in 2020, and includes the layers 'BAYFIELD_HYDRO_2020_LINE' and 'BAYFIELD_HYDRO_2020_POLY'.[This layer contains river data published by the WI Department of Natural Resources (DNR). Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.wi.gov/437/GIS-Metadata]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.bayfieldcounty.wi.gov/892/GIS-Data-Access
